		<div id="comment_body_64118773"><p><div class="quote"><p>most EV's are running 100% on fossil fuel, usually coal</p></div><p>Even if an EV is charged from 100% coal it has 15% better cradle to grave emissions than an ICEV. You think you had a mic drop there but all you did was prove that you don't know shit and haven't done your homework.</p></div>
	</div>

