		<div id="comment_body_64118431"><p><div class="quote"><p>Still waiting...</p></div><p>Just have to point out that it looks like the market in general is moving away from you, so you might be waiting for a while.  It's probably getting harder for you to get an ICE car that meets those requirements.</p></div>
	</div>

